title: Group Discussion for Interviews 101
description: Group Discussion (GD) is a common component of the interview process, especially in competitive job markets. It is designed to assess a candidate's communication skills, teamwork, leadership qualities, and ability to think critically under pressure. This article provides a comprehensive guide to excelling in group discussions during interviews.
